title: Unable to create Discussions
body: Sooo . . . I'm not level 5 on here, but I am level 15 in the game . . . Is this forum supposed to sync up with my in game level?

replies.body: Your Summoner level must not have been synced right with your Boards level, but it looks like it was fixed when you posted here! Go ahead and try posting again elsewhere and seeing if it works. :D
whooooo it worked!!! Yay thank you so much!!! Are you really a fat raccoon?
